      • Tenant

        public Tenant​(String forename,
              String surname,
              String address,
              String phonenumber,
              String birthdate,
              org.salespointframework.useraccount.UserAccount userAccount)
        Constructor of class Tenant
        Parameters:
        forename - of the tenant
        surname - both parameters are used to identify the tenant by name
        address - address of the tenant for physical mailing service as String
        phonenumber - of the tenant as String
        birthdate - of the tenant as String
        userAccount - userAccount of the tenant as class UserAccount given by the Salespoint-Framework containing and saving user data (such as password, email and username)
